text: Henry Junior Plazas Mendoza (born 12 December 1992) is a Venezuelan footballer who plays as a defender for Estudiantes de Mérida in the Venezuelan Primera División. ==References== ==External links== *Profile at World Football Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Estudiantes de Mérida players Category:Aragua FC players Category:Zulia F.C. players Category:Venezuelan Primera División players Category:Venezuelan footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:People from Mérida, Mérida
